snippet.title: BABYMETAL - Distortion (Manly Cover)
snippet.description:
Since BABYMETAL had been first introduced, everyone was in shock and was controversial subject among metal fans for a very long time. But now they have a solid fan base and become one of the most popular metal bands. In fact, although they are far from traditional metal, I like their music. Sometimes I imagine I sing their songs in the middle of their male fans. Only if I could sing so high like a girl. uh... what?

I hope you enjoy my version of the song. Have a nice one!

* Sorry guys, I accidentally exported the video as Mono. I really needed to repost it.

Siegfried Song (Symmetric Chaos, South Korea) - Lead Vocals, Harmony Vocals, Video Editing
Leo Peña (Jotun Studio, Spain) - Keyboards, Bass, Drum Programming, Mixing, Mastering
'WEE' SungHun (MuTrickster, South Korea) - Rhythm and Lead Guitars
Jonatan Storm (Duskfall, Shadowland, Sweden) - Extreme Vocals
